North;;1994;;PG;;Adventure,Comedy,Drama;;4.5;;Rob Reiner;;Elijah Wood,Bruce Willis,Jason Alexander,Julia Louis-Dreyfus,Marc Shaiman,Jussie Smollett,Taylor Fry,Alana Austin,Peg Shirley,Chuck Cooper,Alan Zweibel,Donavon Dietz,Teddy Bergman,Michael Cipriani,Joran Corneal,Joshua Kaplan,James F. Dean,Glenn Walker Harris Jr.;;Eleven-year-old North has had it with his parents. They are always busy with their careers and don't give North the attention he needs, so he files a lawsuit against them. The judge rules that North should either find new parents or return to his own parents within two months. Thus North starts off on a hilarious journey around the world to find the parents that really care about him.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0110687/